pip install .

## ðŸ“š Example Usage

```python
# Import from package 
from quantiletools import quantiles_for_vars, quantiles_by_group

# Example DataFrame
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

df = pd.DataFrame({
    "X1": np.random.randn(10),
    "X2": np.random.randn(10),
    "Group": np.random.choice(["A", "B"], size=10)
})

# Compute quantiles
quantiles_for_vars(df, ["X1", "X2"], probs=[0.1, 0.5, 0.9], qtype=[1, 7])

